name: Nic Carter Raises Concerns on Bitcoin’s Quantum Vulnerability: Q-Day to Arrive by 2035
description: The Priestess of Brass applies the final iridescent seal to the amber heart. Her kinematic prayer attempts to postpone the 2035 intrusion, whispering protection over the vulnerable data key before the quantum winds consume all history and corrode the timeline.
